<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <title>Explore Temples - Divya Darshan</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background: #050e1f; color: white; }
        
        nav {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px 60px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .explore-title {
            text-align: center;
            color: #FFD700;
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .explore-container { 
            display: flex; 
            gap: 35px; 
            padding: 50px; 
            justify-content: center; 
            flex-wrap: wrap; 
        }

        .temple-card { 
            background: white; 
            border-radius: 20px; 
            width: 320px; 
            overflow: hidden; 
            text-align: center; 
            transition: all 0.4s ease; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            color: #081A39;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .temple-card:hover { 
            transform: translateY(-15px); 
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3); 
        }

        .temple-card img { 
            width: 100%; 
            height: 200px; 
            object-fit: cover; 
            border-bottom: 4px solid #FFD700;
        }

        .card-content { padding: 20px; flex-grow: 1; }

        .temple-card h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #081A39; font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; }
        
        .location { color: #ccac00; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 5px 0 15px; text-transform: uppercase; }

        .history-snippet { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: justify; }

        .prasad-tag { 
            background: #f1f5f9; 
            padding: 10px; 
            border-radius: 10px; 
            font-size: 0.85rem; 
            border-left: 4px solid #FFD700;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .prasad-tag strong { color: #081A39; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <a href="/" style="color: #081A39; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;">ॐ Divya Darshan</a>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 25px;">
            <a href="/" style="color: #081A39; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Home</a>
            <a href="/book" style="color: #081A39; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Book Darshan</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="explore-title">Discover Sacred Places</h1>

    <div class="explore-container">
        <a href="/explore/kashi" class="temple-card">
            <img src="/images/kashi.jpg" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1627894483216-2138af692e32?q=80&w=600'">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Kashi Vishwanath</h3>
                <p class="location">Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh</p>
                <p class="history-snippet">Located on the banks of the Ganges, this ancient temple is one of the twelve Jyotirlingas. It is the spiritual heart of India, believed to be the abode of Lord Shiva for eternity.</p>
                <div class="prasad-tag">
                    <strong>Special Prasad:</strong> Banarasi Laddu, Thandai, and Dry Fruits.
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/explore/somnath" class="temple-card">
            <img src="/images/somnath.jpg" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590737150035-7d52a7c4933a?q=80&w=600'">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Somnath Mandir</h3>
                <p class="location">Veraval, Gujarat</p>
                <p class="history-snippet">Known as the 'Eternal Shrine', it is the first of the twelve Jyotirlingas. Standing majestically by the Arabian Sea, it symbolizes the triumph of faith over time and destruction.</p>
                <div class="prasad-tag">
                    <strong>Special Prasad:</strong> Magas (Gram Flour Sweet) and Gujarati Chikki.
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/explore/kedarnath" class="temple-card">
            <img src="/images/kedarnath.jpg" onerror="this.src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1626621341517-bbf3d9990a23?q=80&w=600'">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Kedarnath Dham</h3>
                <p class="location">Rudraprayag, Uttarakhand</p>
                <p class="history-snippet">Nestled in the snow-capped Himalayas, this temple was built by the Pandavas. It is a part of the Char Dham pilgrimage and remains a beacon of divine peace at 3,583 meters altitude.</p>
                <div class="prasad-tag">
                    <strong>Special Prasad:</strong> Garhwali Halwa, Khichdi, and Panchamrit.
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>